---
// About.astro — Bio, headshot, operating model

const principles = [
  "Make authority explicit",
  "Make time first-class",
  "Design for replayability",
  "Separate record from derived view",
  "Align incentives with behaviour",
];
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-16 lg:gap-24">

      <!-- Left column: Bio -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 reveal">
        <p class="text-signal text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4">
          About
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-gradient text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 leading-tight">
          The layer beneath products, where authority and evidence become explicit
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-5 text-text-secondary text-base leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I work on the layer beneath products &mdash; where authority, process, evidence, and incentives need to become explicit. That means designing systems that can hold their shape over time: authority models, provenance, workflow execution, token economies, and the structures that make complex coordination legible and durable.
          </p>
          <p>
            I think in decade-scale systems, then reduce them into clear primitives, annual stages, and execution paths that teams can actually ship.
          </p>
          <p>
            What makes my work unusual is the combination: systems architecture, authority design, workflow modelling, provenance, mechanism design, and commercial reality. Most teams split those concerns across different people. I work across the whole model.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Social links -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mt-8">
          <a href="https://github.com/mattsmithies" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-text-tertiary text-sm hover:text-signal transition-colors">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/mattsmithies" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-text-tertiary text-sm hover:text-signal transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="https://dovu.earth" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-text-tertiary text-sm hover:text-signal transition-colors">DOVU</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column: Photo + Operating model -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 reveal space-y-6">

        <!-- Headshot -->
        <div class="glass-card p-2 overflow-hidden relative">
          <img
            src="/headshot.jpg"
            alt="Matt Smithies"
            class="w-full aspect-[3/4] object-cover object-top rounded-xl brightness-[0.45] contrast-[1.1] saturate-[0.3]"
            loading="lazy"
            onerror="this.parentElement.style.display='none'"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-b from-signal/10 via-transparent to-void/60 mix-blend-screen pointer-events-none"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Operating model -->
        <div class="glass-card p-8">
          <h3 class="text-text-primary font-display font-semibold text-sm tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-6">
            Operating model
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-0">
            {principles.map((principle) => (
              <li class="py-3 border-b border-border last:border-0">
                <span class="text-text-secondary text-sm">{principle}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
